# Project Brief: Eid Greetings Card Generator

## Core Purpose
A bilingual (Arabic/English) web-based application that enables users to create personalized Eid/Ramadan greeting cards through an interactive multi-step process. Each card is customized with a user-selected message and personal name, rendered on company-branded card templates.

## Primary Objectives
1. Provide an intuitive, step-by-step card creation experience
2. Support bilingual interface (Arabic and English) with language-specific content
3. Generate downloadable, personalized greeting cards as PNG images
4. Track card generation analytics via SheetDB integration
5. Support multiple company-branded card templates

## Key Deliverables
- Individual HTML pages for each company card
- Real-time canvas preview of personalized cards
- Multi-step user flow with visual progress indicators
- Language selection and content switching
- Message selection from pre-defined options
- Name personalization
- PNG download functionality
- Responsive design for desktop and mobile

## Scope Boundaries
- **In Scope:**
  - Multi-step card creation flow
  - Bilingual support (Arabic/English)
  - Canvas-based card rendering
  - Company-specific card templates
  - User data tracking
  
- **Out of Scope:**
  - User authentication or accounts
  - Card editing after download
  - Social media sharing integration
  - Custom message input (only pre-defined messages)
  - Multiple card formats (currently PNG only)

## Success Criteria
- Users can successfully create and download personalized cards
- Interface adapts fully to selected language (Arabic or English)
- Cards render correctly with custom fonts and proper text positioning
- Application works seamlessly on mobile and desktop devices
- Card generation data is successfully logged to SheetDB

## Stakeholder Expectations
- Clean, modern UI with navy blue theme
- Smooth user experience with clear step progression
- Fast card generation and download
- Professional appearance of final cards
- Support for multiple company brands
